==建立==
该组织的源頭是來自於2016年[[Vice传媒有限公司|Vice传媒有限公司]]联合创始人、前评论员[[加文·麦金尼斯|加文·麦金尼斯]]在极右翼雜誌《{{link-en|塔基杂志|Taki's Magazine}}》上開的一個笑話，該組織名字取自迪士尼音乐剧《[[阿拉丁|阿拉丁]]》中的歌曲{{en-link|骄傲的男孩|Proud of Your Boy}}<ref name=Vox>{{cite web|last=Coaston|first=Jane|date=2018-10-15|title=The Proud Boys, the bizarre far-right street fighters behind violence in New York, explained|url=https://www.vox.com/2018/10/15/17978358/proud-boys-gavin-mcinnes-manhattan-gop-violence|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181017001652/https://www.vox.com/2018/10/15/17978358/proud-boys-gavin-mcinnes-manhattan-gop-violence|archive-date=2018-10-17|access-date=2020-10-01|website=Vox|dead-url=no}}</ref>。儘管驕傲男孩作為[[另类右派|另類右翼]]運動的一部分出現，但麥金尼斯於2017年初與這項運動保持距離，稱驕傲男孩是“[[另类温和派|另类温和派]]”，而[[另类右派|另類右翼]]的重點是[[美国种族及民族|种族]]<ref name="Marantz">{{cite news |last1=Marantz |first1=Andrew |title=The Alt-Right Branding War Has Torn the Movement in Two |url=http://www.newyorker.com/news/news-desk/the-alt-right-branding-war-has-torn-the-movement-in-two/ |work=The New Yorker |date=2017-07-06 |access-date=2017-08-16 |archive-date=2017-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170810051502/http://www.newyorker.com/news/news-desk/the-alt-right-branding-war-has-torn-the-movement-in-two |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[白人優越主義|白人優越主義]]者的[[2017年团结右翼集会|團結右翼集會]]之後，该组织被进一步重塑<ref name="Woodhouse">{{cite news|last1=Woodhouse|first1=Leighton Akio|title=After Charlottesville, the American Far Right is Tearing Itself Apart|url=https://theintercept.com/2017/09/21/gavin-mcinnes-alt-right-proud-boys-richard-spencer-charlottesville/|access-date=2018-01-10|website=The Intercept|date=2017-09-21|archive-date=2018-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180110234211/https://theintercept.com/2017/09/21/gavin-mcinnes-alt-right-proud-boys-richard-spencer-charlottesville/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[恩里克·塔里奥|恩里克·塔里奥]]自2018年下半年接手骄傲男孩的运营<ref>{{Cite news|last=Shannon|first=Joel|date=30 September 2020|title=Who are the Proud Boys? Far-right group has concerned experts fo