tween pro- and anti-Trump groups|last=Carter|first=Mike|work=[[西雅图时报|Seattle Times]]|date=2017-05-01|access-date=2018-11-13|archive-date=October 30, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181030065212/https://www.seattletimes.com/seattle-news/crime/seattle-police-wary-of-may-day-violence-between-pro-and-anti-trump-groups/|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.splcenter.org/fighting-hate/extremist-files/group/proud-boys|title=Proud Boys|website=Southern Poverty Law Center|access-date=2018-03-18|archive-date=2018-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181016093217/https://www.splcenter.org/fighting-hate/extremist-files/group/proud-boys|deadurl=no}}</ref>。[[全国公共广播电台|全国公共广播电台]]旗下的《{{tsl|en|The Takeaway|这个事情}}》及南方贫困法律中心均将该组织描述为[[仇恨團體|仇恨團體]]<ref>NPR:
